 and Mandatory Birth Control: The CCP's Campaign to Suppress Uyghur Birthrates in Xinjiang|url=https://jamestown.org/product/sterilizations-iuds-and-mandatory-birth-control-the-ccps-campaign-to-suppress-uyghur-birthrates-in-xinjiang/|accessdate=2020-12-01|author=Adrian Zenz|date=|format=|work=|publisher=The Jamestown Foundation|language=en-US|archive-date=2021-12-10|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20211210132447/https://jamestown.org/product/sterilizations-iuds-and-mandatory-birth-control-the-ccps-campaign-to-suppress-uyghur-birthrates-in-xinjiang/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|title=中国“强制新疆维族妇女节育绝育”：敏感话题的七个关键看点|url=https://www.bbc.com/zhongwen/simp/chinese-news-53234038|accessdate=2020-11-30|author=|date=2020-06-30|format=|work=|publisher=英国广播公司|language=zh|archive-date=2021-12-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20211204125547/https://www.bbc.com/zhongwen/simp/chinese-news-53234038|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|title=研究报告指中国强迫维吾尔人做绝育手术|url=https://www.rfi.fr/cn/中国/20200630-研究报告指中国强迫维吾尔人做绝育手术|accessdate=2020-11-30|author=|date=2020-06-30|format=|work=|publisher=法国国际广播电台|language=zh|archive-date=2021-12-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20211204122955/https://www.rfi.fr/cn/%E4%B8%AD%E5%9B%BD/20200630-%E7%A0%94%E7%A9%B6%E6%8A%A5%E5%91%8A%E6%8C%87%E4%B8%AD%E5%9B%BD%E5%BC%BA%E8%BF%AB%E7%BB%B4%E5%90%BE%E5%B0%94%E4%BA%BA%E5%81%9A%E7%BB%9D%E8%82%B2%E6%89%8B%E6%9C%AF|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

2020年8月，[[美国|美国]]的[[唐納·川普|特朗普]]政府据报考虑指控[[中华人民共和国政府|中国政府]]对[[维吾尔人|维吾尔人]]进行“种族灭绝”。<ref>{{Cite news |title=特朗普政府據報考慮指控中國政府對維吾爾人進行“種族滅絕” |url=https://www.voacantonese.com/a/Trump-xinjiang-uighurs-genocide-20200826/5559771.html |publisher=[[美國之音|美國之音]] |date=2020-08-27 |language=zh-hant |accessdate=2020-08-28 |archive-date=2021-03-15 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210315081757/https://www.voacantonese.com/a/Trump-xinjiang-uighurs-genocide-20200826/5559771.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>同一时间，[[美国民主党|美国民主党]][[乔·拜登|拜登]]竞选团队将[[新疆|新疆]]现状定义为“种族灭绝”。<ref>{{Cite news |title=拜登竞选团队将新疆现状定义为“种族灭绝” |url=https://www.voachinese.com/a/Biden-xinjiang-genocide-20200826/5558930.html |publisher=[[美國之音|美國之音]] |date=2020-08-27 |language=zh-hans |accessdate=2020-08-28 |archive-date=2021-03-15 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210315081754/https://www.voachinese.com/a/Biden-xinjiang-genocide-20200826/5558930.html |dead-url=no }}</ref> 

2020年7月和8月，人权组织呼吁[[国际刑事法院|国际刑事法院]]和[[联合国人权理事会|联合国人权理事会]]调查有關中国官员反人类罪和种族灭绝罪的指控<ref name="NYT-ICC">{{Cite news|author=Simons|first=Marlise|date=2020-07-06|title=Uighur Exiles Push for Court Case Accusing China of Genocide|language=en-US|work=The New York Times|url=https://www.nytimes.com/2020/07/06/world/asia/china-xinjiang-uighur-court.html|accessdate=2020-07-08|issn=0362-4331|archivedate=2020-07-10|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20200710011145/https://www.nytimes.com/2020/07/06/world/asia/china-xinjiang-uighur-court.html/}}</ref><ref name="Guardian-ICC">{{Cite news|author=Kuo|first=Lily|date=2020-07-07|title=Exiled Uighurs call on ICC to investigate Chinese 'genocide' in Xinjiang|language=en-GB|work=The Guardian|url=https://www.theguardian.com/world/2020/jul/07/exiled-uighurs-call-on-icc-to-investigate-chinese-genocide-in-xinjiang|accessdate=2020-07-08|issn=0261-3077|archivedate=2020-07-08|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20200708063901/https://www.theguardian.com/world/2020/jul/07/exiled-uighurs-call-on-icc-to-investigate-chinese-genocide-in-xinjiang}}</ref><ref name="AJ-genocide">{{Cite news|url=https://www.aljazeera.com/news/2020/9/15/activists-want-un-to-probe-genocide-of-chinas-uighur-minority|title=Activists want UN to probe 'genocide' of China's Uighur minority|work=[[Al_Jazeera|Al Jazeera]]|date=2020-09-15|accessdate=2020-10-20|archivedate=2020-10-20|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20201020233547/https://www.aljazeera.com/news/2020/9/15/activists-want-un-to-probe-genocide-of-chinas-uighur-minority}}</ref>。2021年1月19日，美国国务卿[[邁克·蓬佩奧|邁克·蓬佩奧]]公开称中国政府對维吾尔人犯下“[[种族灭绝罪|种族灭绝罪]]与[[反人类罪|反人类罪]]”，蓬佩奥的繼任者[[安東尼·布林肯|安東尼·布林肯]]同意蓬佩奥的说法<ref>{{cite news |title=美认定新疆维族遭种族灭绝 新政府表态同意 |url=https://m.dw.com/zh/%E7%BE%8E%E8%AE%A4%E5%AE%9A%E6%96%B0%E7%96%86%E7%BB%B4%E6%97%8F%E9%81%AD%E7%A7%8D%E6%97%8F%E7%81%AD%E7%BB%9D-%E6%96%B0%E6%94%BF%E5%BA%9C%E8%A1%A8%E6%80%81%E5%90%8C%E6%84%8F/a-56281275}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url=https://www.state.gov/determination-of-the-secretary-of-state-on-atrocities-in-xinjiang/ |title=存档副本 |access-date=2021-01-19 |archive-date=2021-01-20 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210120144847/https://www.state.gov/determination-of-the-secretary-of-state-on-atrocities-in-xinjiang/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。对此，[[中华人民共和国外交部|中国外交部]]发言人[[华春莹|华春莹]]表示：“所谓中国在新疆实施种族灭绝和犯反人类罪彻头彻尾就是以蓬佩奥为代表的个别反华反共势力蓄意炮制的耸人听闻的伪命题和恶意荒唐闹剧，只存在于蓬佩奥之流的丑恶政治阴谋中，过去不曾、现在没有、将来也不会发生在中国大地上。”<ref>{{cite news |author=张素 |editor=田博群 |title=华春莹回应蓬佩奥涉疆消极言论：末日小丑和世纪笑话 |url=http://www.chinanews.com/gn/2021/01-20/9392145.shtml |accessdate=2021-01-20 |work=中国新闻网 |date=2021-01-20 |archive-date=2021-01-28 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210128164713/http://www.chinanews.com/gn/2021/01-20/9392145.shtml |dead-url=no }}</ref>

作为对“德国反华学者”郑国恩指控的回应，新疆社会科学院主办的新疆哲学社会科学网发布的研究报告称：“统计数据显示，2010-2018年新疆总人口、少数民族人口、维吾尔族人口均稳步持续增长，新疆汉族人口略有增长。2010-2018年，新疆常住人口从2181.58万人上升至2486.76万人，增加305.18万人，增长13.99%。其中：少数民族人口从1298.59万人上升至1586.08万人，增加287.49万人，增长22.14%；维吾尔族人口从1017.15万人上升至1271.84万人，增加254.69万人，增长25.04%；汉族人口从882.99万人上升至900.68万人，增加17.69万人，增长2.0%。维吾尔族人口的增幅不仅高于全疆人口的增幅，也高于少数民族人口的增幅，更明显高于汉族人口的增幅。”<ref>[http://www.xjass.cn/zxdt/content/2020-09/03/content_522100.htm 关于境外炒作新疆人口问题的研究报告] {{Wayback|url=http://www.xjass.cn/zxdt/content/2020-09/03/content_522100.htm |date=20210228083629 }}，新疆发展研究中心，2020年09月03日</ref>

中国政府的统计数据显示，从2015年到2018年，以维吾尔族为主的[[和田地区|和田地区]]、[[喀什地区|喀什地区]]的出生率由每千人出生人口21.84暴跌60%以上至每千人出生人口8.17。<ref name="apne_Chin">{{Cite news |title=China cuts Uighur births with IUDs, abortion, sterilization |agency=[[Associated_Press|Associated Press]] |date=June 28, 2020 |access-date=December 18, 2020 |url=https://apnews.com/article/269b3de1af34e17c1941a514f78d764c |archive-date=16 December 2020 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201216200613/https://apnews.com/article/269b3de1af34e17c1941a514f78d764c |url-status=live }}</ref>同一时期，全国的出生率从每千人出生人口12.07下降到每千人出生人口10.9，下降了9.69%。中国当局承认2018年新疆的出生率下降了近三分之一，但否认了有关强迫绝育和种族灭绝的报道。<ref name="cnn-fax">{{cite news |last1=CNN |first1=Ivan Watson, Rebecca Wright and Ben Westcott |title=Xinjiang government confirms huge birth rate drop but denies forced sterilization of women |url=https://edition.cnn.com/2020/09/21/asia/xinjiang-china-response-sterilization-intl-hnk/index.html |access-date=26 September 2020 |publisher=CNN |date=21 September 2020 |archive-date=27 September 2020 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200927111925/https://edition.cnn.com/2020/09/21/asia/xinjiang-china-response-sterilization-intl-hnk/index.html |url-status=live }}</ref>2019年，新疆的出生率继续大幅下降，降了近24%，而同一时期全国只降了4.2%。<ref name="apne_Chin"/>

目前，兩任[[美國國務卿|美國國務卿]]——[[邁克·蓬佩奧|蓬佩奧]]<ref name="Pompeo statement 20210119">{{cite news|title=Determination of the Secretary of State on Atrocities in Xinjiang|newspaper=Embassy of the United States, Tbilisi|date=2021-01-19|last=Pompeo|first=Mike|author-link=邁克·蓬佩奧|url=https://ge.usembassy.gov/determination-of-the-secretary-of-state-on-atrocities-in-xinjiang/|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20210123003434/https://ge.usembassy.gov/determination-of-the-secretary-of-state-on-atrocities-in-xinjiang/|archivedate=2021-01-23|accessdate=2021-03-02|dead-url=no}}</ref>和[[安東尼·布林肯|布林肯]]<ref name="Blinken two statements">[[安東尼·布林肯|安東尼·布林肯]]兩次認同蓬佩奧：
