*第二次，1月27日，已就任[[美國國務卿|美國國務卿]]的[[安東尼·布林肯|安東尼·布林肯]]在白宮記者會再次認同蓬佩奧的聲明。{{cite interview|title=Secretary Antony J. Blinken At a Press Availability|work=[[美國國務院|U.S. Department of State]] transcript|first=Anthony J.|last=Blinken|subject-link=安東尼·布林肯|location=Press Briefing Room, Washington, D.C.|date=2021-01-27|url=https://www.state.gov/secretary-antony-j-blinken-at-a-press-availability/|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20210127231828/https://www.state.gov/secretary-antony-j-blinken-at-a-press-availability/|archivedate=2021-01-27|access-date=2021-03-02|dead-url=no}}</ref>、[[加拿大下議院|加拿大下議院]]<ref name="Canada House vote count">{{cite news |title=加拿大國會通過動議指中國對新疆維族進行種族滅絕的決議 |url=https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1576946-20210223.htm |accessdate=2021-02-23 |agency=香港電台 |date=2021-02-22 |archive-date=2021-03-08 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210308040111/https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1576946-20210223.htm |dead-url=no }}</ref>、[[荷蘭下議院|荷蘭下議院]]<ref name="Netherlands vote">*荷蘭語報導：{{cite news|title=Meerderheid Tweede Kamer vindt dat China genocide op Oeigoeren pleegt|newspaper=NU.nl|date=2021-02-25|last=|first=|url=https://www.nu.nl/politiek/6118576/meerderheid-tweede-kamer-vindt-dat-china-genocide-op-oeigoeren-pleegt.html|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20210326063704/https://www.nu.nl/politiek/6118576/meerderheid-tweede-kamer-vindt-dat-china-genocide-op-oeigoeren-pleegt.html|archivedate=2021-03-26|language=nl|accessdate=2021-03-02|dead-url=no}}
